#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:1
msgid "PyRepl 代码执行"
msgstr "PyRepl Code Execution"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:3
msgid ""
"SimpleLLMFunc 提供内置的 PyRepl 支持，允许 LLM 在一个连续上下文中执行 Python "
"代码。与传统的一次性代码执行不同，PyRepl 保持变量和状态，让 LLM 可以分步执行复杂任务。"
msgstr ""
"SimpleLLMFunc includes built-in PyRepl support, allowing LLMs to execute "
"Python code in a continuous context. Unlike one-shot code execution, PyRepl "
"preserves variables and state so the LLM can solve complex tasks step by "
"step."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:5
msgid "功能特性"
msgstr "Features"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:7
msgid ""
"**IPython 子进程后端**：每个 `PyRepl` 实例对应一个独立子进程，内部运行 `IPython InteractiveShell`"
msgstr ""
"**IPython Subprocess Backend**: Each `PyRepl` instance corresponds to an "
"independent subprocess, internally running `IPython InteractiveShell`"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:8
msgid "**连续上下文**：变量在多次调用间持久化，LLM 可以分步执行任务"
msgstr ""
"**Continuous context**: Variables persist across calls, enabling step-by-"
"step execution"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:9
msgid "**实时流式输出**：通过 `event_emitter` 实时获取 stdout/stderr 输出"
msgstr ""
"**Real-time streaming output**: Real-time acquisition of stdout/stderr "
"output via `event_emitter`"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:10
msgid "**异步不阻塞**：代码执行在独立线程运行，不阻塞主事件循环（适合 TUI/流式 UI）"
msgstr ""
"**Async and non-blocking**: Code runs in a dedicated thread and does not "
"block the main event loop (suitable for TUI/streaming UIs)"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:11
msgid "**Session 隔离**：不同的 PyRepl 实例相互独立，互不影响"
msgstr ""
"**Session isolation**: Different PyRepl instances are independent and do not"
" interfere"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:12
msgid "**完整工具集**：提供 execute_code、reset_repl 等工具"
msgstr ""
"**Complete Toolset**: Provides execute_code, reset_repl and other tools"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:13
msgid ""
"**超时保护**：单次 `execute_code` 默认 600 秒活动执行超时；等待 `input()` "
"不计时，且每次收到输入后会重置超时窗口；单次 `input()` 默认 300 秒空闲超时。也可在每次调用时通过 `timeout_seconds` "
"单独覆盖"
msgstr ""
"**Timeout protection**: Single `execute_code` defaults to 600 seconds active"
" execution timeout; waiting for `input()` is not counted, and the timeout "
"window resets after each input is received; single `input()` defaults to 300"
" seconds idle timeout. Can also be separately overridden via "
"`timeout_seconds` in each call."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:14
msgid ""
"**长输出自动截断**：`execute_code` 已启用 `too_long_to_file`，当输出超过 20000 tokens "
"时自动保存到临时文件并截断返回"
msgstr ""
"**Long output auto-truncation**: `execute_code` has enabled "
"`too_long_to_file`, when output exceeds 20000 tokens it automatically saves "
"to a temporary file and returns truncated"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:15
msgid ""
"**Runtime 原语**：通过 `runtime.selfref.history.*` 与 `runtime.selfref.fork.*` "
"暴露受控的 self-reference API"
msgstr ""
"**Runtime primitives**: Expose controlled self-reference API via "
"`runtime.selfref.history.*` and `runtime.selfref.fork.*`"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:16
msgid ""
"**Origin 感知事件流**：每个 `EventYield` 都携带 `origin` 元数据，方便在 TUI 或自定义 UI 中稳定区分主链路和 "
"fork 链路"
msgstr ""
"**Origin-aware Event Stream**: Each `EventYield` carries `origin` metadata, "
"facilitating stable differentiation between the main chain and fork chain in"
" TUI or custom UI"

