#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:388
msgid "将持久记忆追加到 system prompt"
msgstr "Append persistent memory to system prompt"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:390
msgid "这是最常见且推荐的模式：把用户偏好落到 system prompt 记忆中。"
msgstr ""
"This is the most common and recommended pattern: storing user preferences in"
" the system prompt memory."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:404
msgid "也可以直接覆盖 system prompt："
msgstr "You can also directly override the system prompt:"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:410
msgid "常见记忆操作示例"
msgstr "Common Memory Operation Examples"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:429
msgid "Runtime SelfReference 原语参考："
msgstr "Runtime SelfReference Primitives Reference:"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:431
msgid "`runtime.selfref.guide()`: 返回命名空间概览与 fork/记忆最佳实践清单。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.guide()`: Returns namespace overview and fork/memory best "
"practices checklist."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:432
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.keys()`: 列出所有已绑定的 memory key。"
msgstr "`runtime.selfref.history.keys()`: list all bound memory keys."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:433
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.active_key()`: 获取当前执行上下文的 active key。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.active_key()`: Gets the active key of the current "
"execution context."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:434
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.count(key=None)`: 返回当前消息数量。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.count(key=None)`: Returns the current message "
"count."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:435
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.all(key=None)`: 返回全部消息的深拷贝快照。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.all(key=None)`: Returns a deep copy snapshot of all"
" messages."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:436
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.get(index, key=None)`: 读取指定索引消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.get(index, key=None)`: Get message at specified "
"index."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:437
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.append(message, key=None)`: 追加消息到末尾。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.append(message, key=None)`: append message to end."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:438
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.insert(index, message, key=None)`: 在指定位置插入消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.insert(index, message, key=None)`: Insert a message"
" at the specified position."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:439
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.update(index, message, key=None)`: 替换指定索引消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.update(index, message, key=None)`: Replace the "
"message at the specified index."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:440
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.delete(index, key=None)`: 删除指定索引消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.delete(index, key=None)`: Delete the message at the"
" specified index."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:441
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.replace(messages, key=None)`: 用新列表替换全部历史。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.replace(messages, key=None)`: Replace all history "
"with a new list."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:442
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.clear(key=None)`: 清空非 system 消息并保留当前 system prompt。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.clear(key=None)`: Clear non-system messages and "
"retain the current system prompt."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:443
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.get_system_prompt(key=None)`: 读取最新 system prompt "
"文本。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.get_system_prompt(key=None)`: reads the latest "
"system prompt text."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:444
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.set_system_prompt(text, key=None)`: 覆盖当前 system "
"prompt。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.set_system_prompt(text, key=None)`: Overrides the "
"current system prompt."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:445
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.append_system_prompt(text, key=None)`: 追加 system "
"prompt 文本。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.append_system_prompt(text, key=None)`: append "
"system prompt text."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:446
msgid "`runtime.selfref.fork.spawn(message, ...)`: 异步创建子 fork（chat 形态）。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.fork.spawn(message, ...)`: Asynchronously create child fork"
" (chat form)."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:447
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.fork.gather_all(fork_id_or_list=None, "
"include_history=False)`: 聚合 fork 结果，返回 `dict[fork_id -> ForkResult]`（用 "
"`.items()`/`.values()` 遍历）。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.fork.gather_all(fork_id_or_list=None, "
"include_history=False)`: Aggregate fork results, return `dict[fork_id -> "
"ForkResult]` (use `.items()`/`.values()` to iterate)."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:449
msgid ""
"默认情况下 fork 结果为紧凑模式，仅返回 "
"`fork_id`、`memory_key`、`response`、`history_count`、`history_included=False` "
"等元数据。 只有确实需要子历史时才设置 `include_history=True`。"
msgstr ""
"By default, fork results are in compact mode, returning only metadata such "
"as `fork_id`, `memory_key`, `response`, `history_count`, and "
"`history_included=False`. Only set `include_history=True` when you actually "
"need the child history."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:452
msgid "Fork 规划清单（`runtime.selfref.guide()` 会返回同样的 guidance）："
msgstr ""
"Fork planning checklist (`runtime.selfref.guide()` will return the same "
"guidance):"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:454
msgid "每一层 agent 只做本层规划，执行下放给子 fork。"
msgstr ""
"Each agent layer only performs planning at its own layer, delegating "
"execution to child forks."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:455
msgid "无依赖的任务尽量并行 `fork.spawn(...)`。"
msgstr ""
"Tasks without dependencies should be parallelized as much as possible using "
"`fork.spawn(...)`."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:456
msgid "fork 前先整理记忆：弱相关信息先总结或落盘。"
msgstr ""
"Before forking, organize memory first: summarize or persist weak related "
"information first."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:457
msgid "fork 提示词写清完成边界和验收标准，优先文件+回传消息交接。"
msgstr ""
"Clearly state the completion boundaries and acceptance criteria in the fork "
"prompt, prioritizing file + return message handover."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:458
msgid "fork 结果默认是紧凑模式；需要子历史时再按需 `include_history=True`。"
msgstr ""
"The fork result is in compact mode by default; when you need child history, "
"set `include_history=True` on demand."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:459
msgid "每个里程碑后回收并整理记忆，再进入下一阶段。"
msgstr ""
"After each milestone, retrieve and organize memories, then enter the next "
"phase."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:461
msgid "清理记忆的注意事项："
msgstr "Notes on memory cleanup:"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:463
msgid "使用 `reset_repl` 清理 REPL 命名空间中的 Python 变量。"
msgstr "Use `reset_repl` to clean Python variables in the REPL namespace."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:464
msgid ""
"需要清理记忆时，使用 `runtime.selfref.history.delete(...)` 或 "
"`runtime.selfref.history.replace(...)`。"
msgstr ""
"When you need to clear memory, use `runtime.selfref.history.delete(...)` or "
"`runtime.selfref.history.replace(...)`."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:465
msgid "需要保留当前 system prompt 时，使用 `runtime.selfref.history.clear(...)`。"
msgstr ""
"To retain the current system prompt, use "
"`runtime.selfref.history.clear(...)`."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:467
msgid ""
"所有操作都会写入 `SelfReference` 的内部存储，而不是直接暴露原始列表。单次对话中的记忆变更会在回合结束时合并进返回的 "
"`updated_history`（事件模式下为 `ReactEndEvent.final_messages`）。"
msgstr ""
"All operations are written to the internal storage of `SelfReference`, "
"rather than directly exposing the original list. Memory changes in a single "
"conversation will be merged into the returned `updated_history` at the end "
"of the turn (in event mode, it's `ReactEndEvent.final_messages`)."

